/* ==UserStyle==
@name         YouTube (Classic) | Dark FADE (2020)
@namespace    de.sidneys.userstyles
@version      1.6.0
@description  The sought-after DARK FADE style for the classic YouTube interface. Actively maintained fork of the original. Use the "Good Old YouTube" browser extension to switch back to classic YouTube.
